name: This Is Outrageous!
Lore: '''I recommend a commission be sent to Naboo to ascertain the truth!''',
Text: 'Deploy on table. If no senator here, you may place a senator here from hand to cancel an opponent''s Force drain. If a trade agenda here, once during your turn, you may place a card from hand in Lost Pile, shuffle that pile, and take top card into hand.',
